    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（深夜。中庭に出ると、寮の方から不気味な音楽や）\n（悲鳴が聞こえてきたので、リビングに向かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Late at night‚ I walk into the yard and hear ominous music and screams)\n(from the dorm‚ so I head to the living room to see what’s going on.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
      "startTime": 14.366666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あ、{user}さん\nど、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ {user}-san.\nS-something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、庭に出たら悲鳴とおぞましい音楽が\n聞こえてきたから気になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I heard screams and eerie music from outside‚\nso I just wanted to check if anything's wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ご、ごめんなさい……多分……映画観てて\n悲鳴上げちゃったんだと……思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ s-sorry about that. I was the one who screamed\nwhile watching this movie… I think.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "その……明日はお休みですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is… tomorrow was our day off‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃんけんで勝った人のお勧め映画を\nみんなで一気観しよう！　って話になったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so we did rock-paper-scissors‚ and the winner\ngot to pick all the movies we’d watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "結局、私が勝って借りてきたんですが\n全部ホラー映画だったので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won‚ so I rented some for us.\nBut they’re all horror movies…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな怖いの無理ー！\nって部屋に戻っちゃったんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The others were like \"too scary!\"\nand they ran off back to their rooms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、選んだの私だし\nちゃんと全部観ないとって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I chose the films‚\nso I have to watch all of them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……千紗も盛り上がると思って\n選んだんだろうけど、無理しなくていいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. But you chose them thinking everyone would enjoy them‚ right?\nYou don’t have to force yourself to watch them all alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことありません\n無理なんて……全然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m not.\nI’m not forcing myself… not at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私……\n実は大好きなんです、ホラー映画",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides…\nI love horror movies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "…………えっ\nそうだったのか？　意外な趣味だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?\nYou do? That’s a little unexpected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに意外だってよく言われます……\nでも、洋画邦画関係なく、わりと観る方で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I h-heard that a lot.\nBut I’ll watch pretty much any horror film.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "ジャンルも、オカルトからサイコ\nスプラッターやパニックもの、ゾンビものまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Any genre from any country. Occult‚ slasher‚\nsplatter‚ panic‚ zombie‚ the lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "ホラー映画って、観てるとなんだか\n前向きになれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you think watching horror movies\nmakes you feel kinda positive about everything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "……大体が凄く怖い事件に\n巻き込まれて、みんな逃げ惑いますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These people get caught up in scary stuff\nand run around in terror and panic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "主人公達って最後まで諦めないで\n死の恐怖に打ち勝とうとするじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the main character never gives up‚\ntrying to overcome the fear of death.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういう人達を見てると\nなんだかこう……前向きになれる気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watching people like that\nmakes me feel more positive for some reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "変……でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that… strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分かるような分からないような……\nでもまあ、映画の楽しみ方は人それぞれだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I kinda understand and kinda don’t…\nBut everyone enjoys different things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは、その……\nホラー映画って観ないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about you‚ {user}-san…\nDo you watch horror movies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "観なくはないけど……\nそこまで大好きというほどでもないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ sure.\nBut I’m not a real lover like you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあホラー映画中級者ぐらい、かな？\nふむふむ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An intermediate horror fan‚ maybe?\nHmmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "だとしたら、最初は3怖ぐらいの映画の方が\nお勧めかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ maybe I’d go with a movie\nthat’s level 3 on the scary scale to start with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……3怖？\nカレー屋さんの3辛みたいなものか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Level 3?\nIs that like the Scoville scale they have at curry houses?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私が自分で分類する時に使ってるんです\n全部で10怖まであります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It’s a rating I made up myself.\nIt goes all the way up to level 10.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは洋画派ですか？\nそれとも邦画派ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ do you like western films\nor Japanese films?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
