      "text": "できれば出ない方がいい……かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d rather not watch a ghost film… I guess.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあどれにしようかな\nえへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Which one to choose…\nHehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "……よし、これに決めました\nせっかくですから一緒に観ませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ this one.\nWhy don’t we watch it together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "レンタル明日までですし、オススメしたい映画も\nちょうどあったので……ダメでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got it rented until tomorrow‚ and it’s one\nI’d definitely recommend. What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ\n千紗が勧めてくれるなら、ぜひ観てみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure thing.\nIf Chisa recommend it‚ I’m down to check it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます……！\nじゃ、じゃあさっそく再生しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nI’m hitting the play button.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
