      "text": "えへへ、嬉しいです。ホラー映画を\n一緒に観てくれる友達、いなかったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ this is great. I’ve never really had\nfriends I can watch horror films with before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_01-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "本当はこういう趣味って良くないのかな\nって思うことも……あったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes I even wonder…\nif this is much of a hobby at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
